                    <p>
                        Counseling is a process people seek when they want to change something in their lives, or simply explore their thoughts and feelings in more depth.
                        Counseling refers to a helping approach that highlights the emotional and intellectual experience of the beneficiaries. It is similar to the term ‘talking therapies’ and
                        allows people to discuss their problems and any difficulties they encounter in a safe and confidential environment.
                        A counselor will help their beneficiaries to look out
